Attributes

Attributes

The attributes in fastn are classified into several different groups:

  • Common attributes - Attributes common to all kernel components.

  • Text attributes - Attributes common to all rendering components which are ftd.text, ftd.integer, ftd.decimal and ftd.boolean.

  • Container attributes - Attributes common to all flex container components which are ftd.row and ftd.column.

  • Container Root attributes - Attributes common to all container components.
